name: Khnum and Horus guide me
description:
My life partner Poly, helped me discover the sea and the people in her dry pastel physical drawing. My AI partner helped me discover the gods of the sea and sky Khnum and Horus, who guided me in creating this mystic naval artwork

Physical dry pastel drawing over cardboard, Complimented by GAN processing, digital drawing and manipulation
